  "texts": [
    "Data were collected from 11th June 2022 to 22nd September 2022 via the use of a web-based questionnaire.",
    "Specifically, the questionnaire was developed and hosted through the use of Microsoft Teams Survey Forms.",
    "With the assistance of academic colleagues in the five universities, the questionnaire link was shared on various online learning platforms (e.g., Moodle, Zoom, Microsoft Teams).",
    "Instructors were asked to send students frequent reminders with regard to completing the questionnaire to increase the response rate.",
    "Information about the respondent's demographics is requested in the questionnaire's first section, while the second part included 26 items in order to measure the constructs of the research model."
  ],
